plate is about 11,000 meters in diameter. This orion is<br>
 also 10,000 meters in length, and 10,000 meters in <br>
width above  the 11000 meter impulse absorber <br>
system. To put it in English imperiel units it is about<br>
 6 miles long, and 6 miles wide. Two dimensionaly that is<br>
36 sqaure miles. In three dimensions it is 216 Cubic miles<br>
